					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-655428#post-2197288</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-655428/scp-1846#post-2197288</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 06 Jan 2015 06:03:56 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ambassador Throz</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1596956</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Has it occurred to nobody else that corn is a human invention? It literally cannot propagate without human farming, and was probably bred over thousands of years out of a species of south american grass. It makes this whole SCP that much weirder - the &quot;only god&quot; is one of a plant that humans invented? Why is there even a god of the stuff at all if it's effectively the world's oldest GMO?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
